  "3184960": {
    "name": "抵抗者",
    "steam_appid": 3184960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在那黑暗岁月，我们早已习惯生离死别。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >侵略者的铁蹄踏碎山河，每一寸土地燃烧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是驰骋在林海雪原，不屈的抗联；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是隐谧在绝境的孤岛，永不消逝的电波；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是翻腾在运河的波涛，快意恩仇的尖刀；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是屹立在太行之巅，血肉筑起的长城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿起武器，我们是抵抗者！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏场景：重返历史的危机时刻</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们踏上的，是以热血浸透的土地。从肃杀苍茫的林海雪原，到戒备森严的城镇街巷，再到危机四伏的敌后村庄...在这里，你  将体验到沉郁悲壮、波谲云诡的抗战氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/2cb94a99fff5603ae65fafab7fd21c4d.poster.avif?t=1769698621\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/2cb94a99fff5603ae65fafab7fd21c4d.webm?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/2cb94a99fff5603ae65fafab7fd21c4d.mp4?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏关卡：沉浸式的关卡体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里的一草一木、一砖一瓦，都在无声地诉说着当年那段波澜壮阔的历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/83ddfea612d84ef259210b71c38153b8.poster.avif?t=1769698621\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/83ddfea612d84ef259210b71c38153b8.webm?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/83ddfea612d84ef259210b71c38153b8.mp4?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗枪械：每一把武器都是历史的回响</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲手操作历史的证物，你握住的不仅仅是武器，更是穿越百年的战场记忆。游戏中可以使用几十种枪械，包含各式步枪、冲锋枪、手枪、机枪，有经典的“汉阳造”、传奇的“盒子炮”和“花机关”，还有那些在中国近代史中涌现的各式武器...它们终将化为你的战斗本能，助你在危机四伏的战场上杀出一条血路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/d79b67737f0445becd1f8db9615c0fb4.poster.avif?t=1769698621\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/d79b67737f0445becd1f8db9615c0fb4.webm?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/d79b67737f0445becd1f8db9615c0fb4.mp4?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗玩法：紧张刺激的战场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当敌人的探照灯划破夜空，当复仇的利器刺向侵略者……当这一切在眼前再现，你将不再是历史的旁观者。这不是一段被尘封的记忆，而是血脉中随时会被唤醒的共鸣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/2ac40802584d7d3f9cabda886828c610.poster.avif?t=1769698621\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/2ac40802584d7d3f9cabda886828c610.webm?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184960/extras/2ac40802584d7d3f9cabda886828c610.mp4?t=1769698621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现在，轮到你成为那段黑暗岁月中的光、成为历史本身。</strong></p>",
